---
---
<section class="about" id="wir" aria-label="Über Miette und Nicolai">
  <div class="about__inner">

    <!-- Visual side -->
    <div class="about__visual">
      <div class="about__frame reveal">
        <img
          src="/images/about/miette und nicolai.jpg"
          alt="Miette und Nicolai — MiNi Photography"
          loading="lazy"
          width="800"
          height="1000"
          class="about__main-img"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="about__accent reveal reveal--delay-2">
        <img
          src="/images/gallery/04.jpg"
          alt=""
          loading="lazy"
          width="400"
          height="500"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="about__tag reveal reveal--delay-3" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="about__tag-number">200<span class="about__tag-plus">+</span></span>
        <span class="about__tag-label">glückliche Paare</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Text side -->
    <div class="about__content">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="section-label">Wir sind MiNi</span>
        <h2 class="about__title">
          Zwei Menschen.<br />
          <em>Eine Leidenschaft.</em>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="about__text reveal reveal--delay-1">
        <p>
          Wir sind Miette und Nicolai — ein Paar, das sich in die Fotografie verliebt hat.
          Und weil wir selbst wissen, wie sich ein besonderer Moment anfühlt, wollen wir
          genau das festhalten: nicht das perfekte Foto, sondern den echten Augenblick.
        </p>
        <p>
          Keine starren Posen. Kein inszeniertes Lächeln. Nur euch — so wie ihr wirklich seid.
        </p>
      </div>

      <ul class="about__highlights reveal reveal--delay-2" aria-label="Was uns ausmacht">
        <li class="about__highlight">
          <span class="about__check" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          Zu zweit fotografiert
        </li>
        <li class="about__highlight">
          <span class="about__check" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          Rhein-Main &amp; Destination Weddings
        </li>
        <li class="about__highlight">
          <span class="about__check" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          Authentisch statt inszeniert
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="reveal reveal--delay-3">
        <a href="/ueber-uns" class="about__cta">
          Mehr über uns erfahren
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/>
            <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.about {
  padding: clamp(5rem, 12vh, 10rem) 0;
  background: var(--color-parchment);
  overflow: hidden;
}

.about__inner {
  max-width: var(--container-max);
  margin-inline: auto;
  padding-inline: var(--container-gutter);
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 8rem);
  align-items: center;
}

/* ── Visual side ──────────────────────────────── */
.about__visual {
  position: relative;
  padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
}

.about__frame {
  aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
  overflow: hidden;
  max-width: 420px;
}

.about__main-img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: top center;
  transition: transform 0.8s ease;
}
.about__frame:hover .about__main-img { transform: scale(1.03); }

.about__accent {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  right: 0;
  width: 46%;
  aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(30, 24, 23, 0.22);
  border: 4px solid var(--color-parchment);
}

.about__accent img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: center;
}

.about__tag {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 2.5rem;
  left: -1.5rem;
  background: var(--color-bark);
  color: var(--color-cream);
  padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.15rem;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(30, 24, 23, 0.2);
}

.about__tag-number {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1;
  color: var(--color-cream);
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.about__tag-plus {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.2;
  color: var(--color-clay);
}

.about__tag-label {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 0.58rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255, 252, 250, 0.55);
}

/* ── Text side ────────────────────────────────── */
.about__content {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3vh, 2.5rem);
}

.about__title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 3.8vw, 3.4rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  color: var(--color-ink);
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}
.about__title em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--color-clay);
}

.about__text {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
}
.about__text p {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 0.94rem;
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.85;
  color: var(--color-bark);
}

.about__highlights {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.8rem;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--color-sand);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-sand);
  padding: 1.5rem 0;
}

.about__highlight {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.8rem;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 0.86rem;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--color-ink);
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
}

.about__check {
  color: var(--color-clay);
  flex-shrink: 0;
  display: flex;
}

.about__cta {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 0.76rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--color-bark);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-sand);
  padding-bottom: 0.22rem;
  transition: color 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;
}
.about__cta:hover {
  color: var(--color-clay);
  border-bottom-color: var(--color-clay);
}

/* ── Responsive ───────────────────────────────── */
@media (max-width: 860px) {
  .about__inner {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .about__visual {
    max-width: 460px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  .about__tag {
    left: 0;
  }
}
</style>
